    <briefdescription>
<para>Manages score pools and processes score commands. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1scoring_1_1ScorePoolManager" kindref="compound">ScorePoolManager</ref> is responsible for creating and managing score pools, and for handling score update commands. It implements both the Manager interface (for lifecycle management) and ScoreCommandHandler (for receiving score commands from the command system).</para>
<para>Score updates are batched: commands submitted via `submit()` are queued and processed during `flush()`, ensuring deterministic ordering.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1scoring_1_1ScorePool" kindref="compound">ScorePool</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
